## ðŸš€ Running the Game

No build step required.

### Option 1: Open directly
Simply open `CUBE4.html` in a modern browser.

### Option 2: Serve locally (recommended)
Some browsers restrict ES module imports when opening files directly.

```bash
cd cube4
python3 -m http.server
